          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Border Airport Fairness Act of &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;b&gt;2023&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires the President to designate certain primary airports near the border as ports of entry and terminate the user fee requirement for customs services at these airports.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
